1,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8826d9c4e1407d9cfec3c9baeed79d201a8884ea","tid":2446252,"uid":365800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"因為有配額所以要購買配額 令到每件貨品增加相同嘅固定成本 咁本身貴嘅產品(好產品)相對成本就會低咗 靚嘢更多人去買<br />\n利申：唔肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"如果真係要 買配額 既話 咁你岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知以前香港比人配額成衣係唔係咁玩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:06:23.000Z","msg":"此post已完，呢種配額的確係買，所以可以apply到Alchian law"},{"pid":"514929af53d9390bc94b00979af444a38336860c","tid":2446252,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"Let P be profit per product, C be cost per product<br />\n配額成本 be C1<br />\n<br />\nwe would like to maximise profit / cost<br />\nnew profit/ new cost  =  (<strong>P</strong>-<em>C1</em>)/(C+<em>C1</em>)<br />\nSuppose <strong>P</strong>/<strong>C</strong> is constant <em>C2 </em>over all product,<br />\nthen (<strong>P</strong>-<em>C1</em>)/(<strong>C</strong>+<em>C1</em>) = (<strong>C</strong> <em>C2 </em>- <em>C1</em>) (<strong>C</strong> + <em>C1</em>)<br />\nto maximise profit / cost, we take <strong>C</strong> tends to infinity<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 張五常經濟學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e6b2b73dd9c5ce4d96f1b4493ba818260d0950","tid":2446252,"uid":31291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d704267c3d32d2697bb5659b9f396d6f743d97a","tid":2446252,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e5bc3df10208fb0d9282585714923e44e1735f9","tid":2446252,"uid":31291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209695dcbbae6eecd1d97195aabd2153c6efac5f","tid":2446252,"uid":249094,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:24:32.000Z","msg":"A/B&gt;(A+x)/(B+x), whenA,B,x&gt;0"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"可否解釋配額點解會導致+x?<br />\nper unit tax我仲明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"quota rent"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"點解高質貨同低質貨既價格都上升左一樣既數字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nquota rent就我所知係quota後既價格變化*交易量"},{"pid":"a72c6cf76e5881af3460e988f9d6c158da0b9d3d","tid":2446252,"uid":113532,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f66bebff0673e4928bb9029bc3776a5d208a6041","tid":2446252,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"因為你唔比人入更多貨<br />\n人地賣貴貨先可以賺更多<br />\n貴貨通常高質<br />\n利申：10年dse econ5** 選我正解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:11:05.000Z","msg":"你個回答係正解，但DSE 12年先第一屆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"edb0af230a37ced189ae9351f5ec234e88c9275b","tid":2446252,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:30:35.000Z","msg":"應該睇張五常 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依條link解答咗好多依個post嘅問題，例如香港係當年亞洲唯一可以自由買賣成衣配額嘅地方<br />\n因為配額有價值，無論出口高質素嘅衫定係低質素嘅衫都要用到配額，所以喺中學程度可以用Relative price去解釋<br />\n<a href=\"http://nscheung.blogspot.com/2003/11/blog-post_26.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnscheung.blogspot.com%2F2003%2F11%2Fblog-post_26.html&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfHvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=74849fc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://nscheung.blogspot.com/2003/11/blog-post_26.html</a>"}}